Had a celebratory cupcake with myself this afternoon. Just got done shooting for a new Kendra Scott store on my first day of my new internship! I'm officially working with Fashion X Austin as a social media intern with a focus in photography. I get to not only shoot promotional events like today, but I'll be doing fashion photography for their Instagram/website, get to learn & work with professional photographers on editorial shoots AND attend Austin Fashion Week. After being handed lots of "NOs" in the last few weeks I'm so happy they said "YES" and let me join their stylish team. I'm so excited to see where this goes!
